or mobile-edge cloud computing (2016) IEEE/ACM Trans. Netw., 24 (5), pp. 2795-2808. , Oct; Bernstein, D., Containers and cloud: From LXC to docker to kubernetes (2014) Ieee Cloud Comput., 1 (3), pp. 81-84. , Sep; Wang, L., Jiao, L., Li, J., Muhlhauser, M., Online resource allocation for arbitrary user mobility in distributed edge clouds (2017) Proc. Ieee 37th Int. Conf. Distrib. Comput. Syst. (ICDCS), pp. 1281-1290. , Jun; Grant, M., Boyd, S., (2014) CVX: Matlab Software for Disciplined Convex Programming, Version 2.1, , http://cvxr.com/cvx; (2014) Inc. Gurobi Optimizer Reference Manual, 2015. , http://www.gurobi.com, GUROBI OPTIMIZATION; Ye, Y., (2011) Interior Point Algorithms: Theory and Analysis, 44. , Hoboken, NJ, USA: Wiley; Sutton, R.S., Barto, A.G., (2018) Reinforcement Learning: An Introduction., , Cambridge, MA, USA: MIT Press; Chen, X., Han, Z., Zhang, H., Xue, G., Xiao, Y., Bennis, M., Wireless resource scheduling in virtualized radio access networks using stochastic learning (2018) Ieee Trans. Mobile Comput., 17 (4), pp. 961-974. , Apr; He, H., Shan, H., Huang, A., Ye, Q., Zhuang, W., Edge-Aided computing and transmission scheduling for LTE-U-Enabled IoT (2020) Ieee Trans. Wireless Commun., , early access, Aug. 25; Kachroo, P., Özbay, K., (1999) Feedback Control Theory for Dynamic Traffic Assignment., , Cham, Switzerland: Springer; Liang, L., Ye, H., Li, G.Y., Spectrum sharing in vehicular networks based on multi-Agent reinforcement learning (2019) Ieee J. Sel. Areas Commun., 37 (10), pp. 2282-2292. , Oct; Boyd, S., Boyd, S.P., Vandenberghe, L., (2004) Convex Optimization, , Cambridge, U.K.: Cambridge Univ. Press},
