yst. Cham, Switzerland: Springer, pp. 66-83; Jiang, W., Feng, G., Qin, S., Liang, Y.-C., Learning-based cooperative content caching policy for mobile edge computing (2019) Proc. IEEE Int. Conf. Commun. (ICC), pp. 1-6. , May; Nguyen, K.K., Duong, T.Q., Vien, N.A., Le-Khac, N.-A., Nguyen, M.-N., Non-cooperative energy efficient power allocation game in D2D communication: A multi-agent deep reinforcement learning approach (2019) IEEE Access, 7, pp. 100480-100490; Zhang, Z., Zhang, D., Qiu, R.C., Deep reinforcement learning for power system applications: An overview (2020) CSEE J. Power Energy Syst., 6 (1), pp. 213-225; Ke, H., Wang, J., Wang, H., Ge, Y., Joint optimization of data offloading and resource allocation with renewable energy aware for IoT devices: A deep reinforcement learning approach (2019) IEEE Access, 7, pp. 179349-179363; Polyanskiy, Y., Poor, H.V., Verdu, S., Channel coding rate in the finite blocklength regime (2010) IEEE Trans. Inf. Theory, 56 (5), pp. 2307-2359. , May; Durisi, G., Koch, T., Popovski, P., Toward massive, ultrareliable, and low-latency wireless communication with short packets (2016) Proc. IEEE, 104 (9), pp. 1711-1726. , Sep; She, C., Yang, C., Available range of different transmission modes for ultra-reliable and low-latency communications (2017) Proc. IEEE 85th Veh. Technol. Conf. (VTC Spring), pp. 1-5. , Jun; Chen, B., Yang, C., Caching policy optimization for D2D communica-tions by learning user preference (2017) Proc. IEEE 85th Veh. Technol. Conf. (VTC Spring), pp. 1-6. , Jun; Liu, T., Development and application of electrical equipment intelligent detection management system (2020) Proc. 5th Int. Conf. Smart Grid Electr. Automat. (ICSGEA), pp. 70-73. , Jun; Hu, S., Chen, X., Ni, W., Wang, X., Hossain, E., Modeling and analysis of energy harvesting and smart grid-powered wireless communication networks: A contemporary survey (2020) IEEE Trans. Green Commun. Netw., 4 (2), pp. 461-496. , Jun; Bu, F., Chang, D.E., Double prioritized state recycled experience replay (2020) Proc. IEEE Int. Conf. Consum. Electron.-Asia (ICCE-Asia), pp. 1-6. , Nov; Alfakih, T., Hassan, M.M., Gumaei, A., Savaglio, C., Fortino, G., Task offloading and resource allocation for mobile edge computing by deep reinforcement learning based on SARSA (2020) IEEE Access, 8, pp. 54074-54084; Shanmugam, K., Golrezaei, N., Dimakis, A.G., Molisch, A.F., Caire, G., FemtoCaching: Wireless content delivery through distributed caching helpers (2013) IEEE Trans. Inf. Theory, 59 (12), pp. 8402-8413. , Dec; Chen, X., Zhang, H., Wu, C., Mao, S., Ji, Y., Bennis, M., Optimized computation offloading performance in virtual edge computing systems via deep reinforcement learning (2019) IEEE Internet Things J., 6 (3), pp. 4005-4018. , Jun; Cao, X., Wan, H., Lin, Y., Han, S., High-value prioritized experience replay for off-policy reinforcement learning (2019) Proc. IEEE 31st Int. Conf. Tools with Artif. Intell. (ICTAI), pp. 1510-1514. , Nov; Liu, Z., Chen, X., Chen, Y., Li, Z., Deep reinforcement learning based dynamic resource allocation in 5G ultra-dense networks (2019) Proc. IEEE Int. Conf. Smart Internet Things (SmartIoT), pp. 168-174. , Aug; Zhang, Y., Di, B., Zheng, Z., Lin, J., Song, L., Distributed multi-cloud multi-access edge computing by multi-agent reinforcement learning (2021) IEEE Trans. Wireless Commun., 20 (4), pp. 2565-2578. , Apr},
