Softw. Eng., 38 (4), pp. 755-777. , 2012; Monderer, D., Shapley, L.S., Fictitious play property for games with identical interests (1996) J. Econ. Theor., 68 (1), pp. 258-265. , 1996; Moser, O., Rosenberg, F., Dustdar, S., Domain-specific service selection for composite services (2012) IEEE Trans. Softw. Eng., 38 (4), pp. 828-843. , 2012; Moustafa, A., Zhang, M., Multi-objective service composition using reinforcement learning (2013) Service-Oriented Computing, pp. 298-312. , Springer; Nash, J., Non-cooperative games (1951) Ann. Math., 54 (2), pp. 286-295. , 1951; Oh, S.-C., Lee, D., Kumara, S.R.T., Effective web service composition in diverse and large-scale service networks (2008) IEEE Trans. Serv. Comput., 1 (1), pp. 15-32. , 2008; Oh, S.-C., Lee, D., Kumara, S.R.T., Effective web service composition in diverse and large-scale service networks (2008) IEEE Trans. Serv. Comput., 1 (1), pp. 15-32. , http://dx.doi.org/10.1109/TSC.2008.1, 2008; Panait, L., Luke, S., Cooperative multi-agent learning: The state of the art (2005) Proceedings of 2005 Autonomous Agents and Multi-Agent Systems (AAMAS'05), pp. 387-434; Papadopoulos, P., Tianfield, H., Moffat, D., Barrie, P., Decentralized multi-agent service composition (2013) Multiagent Grid Syst., 9 (1), pp. 45-100. , 2013; Pistore, M., Marconi, A., Bertoli, P., Traverso, P., Automated composition of web services by planning at the knowledge level (2005) IJCAI, 19, pp. 1252-1259; Pistore, M., Traverso, P., Bertoli, P., Automated composition of web services by planning in asynchronous domains (2005) ICAPS, 5, pp. 2-11; Puterman, M.L., (2014) Markov Decision Processes: Discrete Stochastic Dynamic Programming, , John Wiley & Sons, New York, NY; Salehie, M., Tahvildari, L., Self-adaptive software: Landscape and research challenges (2009) ACM Trans. Auton. Adapt. Syst., 4 (2), p. 14. , 2009; Shin, D.-H., Lee, K.-H., Suda, T., Automated generation of composite web services based on functional semantics (2009) Web Semant.: Sci. Serv. Agents World Wide Web, 7 (4), pp. 332-343. , 2009; Singh, S., Jaakkola, T., Littman, M.L., Szepesvári, C., Convergence results for single-step on-policy reinforcement-learning algorithms (2000) Mach. Learn., 38 (3), pp. 287-308. , 2000; Stone, P., Veloso, M., Multiagent systems: A survey from a machine learning perspective (2000) Auton. Robots, 8 (3), pp. 345-383. , 2000; Sutton, R.S., Barto, A.G., (1998) Reinforcement Learning: An Introduction, 1. , Cambridge University Press, Cambridge; Tong, H., Cao, J., Zhang, S., Li, M., A distributed algorithm for web service composition based on service agent model (2011) IEEE Trans. Parallel Distrib. Syst., 22 (12), pp. 2008-2021. , 2011; Vogel, T., Giese, H., Model-driven engineering of self-adaptive software with EUREMA (2014) ACM Transactions on Autonomous and Adaptive Systems (TAAS), 8 (4), p. 18. , 2014; Wang, C.-Y., Chen, W.-W., Yao, L., A multi-agent cooperative reinforcement learning algorithm based on team markov game (2004) J. Fudan Univ., 5, p. 041. , 2004; Wang, H., Chen, X., Wu, Q., Yu, Q., Zheng, Z., Bouguettaya, A., Integrating onpolicy reinforcement learning with multi-agent techniques for adaptive service composition (2014) Service- Oriented Computing, pp. 154-168. , Springer; Wang, H., Wang, X., Zhang, X., Yu, Q., Hu, X., Effective service composition using multi-agent reinforcement learning (2016) Knowl.-Based Syst., 92, pp. 151-168. , 2016; Wang, H., Wang, X., Zhou, X., Amulti-agent reinforcement learning model for service composition (2012) Proceedings of the 2012 IEEE Ninth International Conference on Services Computing (SCC'12), pp. 681-682. , IEEE; Wang, H., Wu, Q., Chen, X., Yu, Q., Integrating Gaussian process with reinforcement learning for adaptive service composition (2015) Service-Oriented Computing, pp. 203-217. , Springer; Wang, H., Wu, Q., Chen, X., Yu, Q., Zheng, Z., Bouguettaya, A., Adaptive and dynamic service composition via multi-agent reinforcement learning (2014) Proceedings of th