borative Learning, 5 (3), pp. 255-258; VanLehn, K., The behavior of tutoring systems (2006) International Journal of Artificial Intelligence in Education, 16 (3), pp. 227-265; VanLehn, K., Regulative Loops, Step Loops and Task Loops (2015) International Journal of Artificial Intelligence in Education, , Online First; Woolf, B.P., Building intelligent interactive tutors: Student-centered strategies for revolutionizing e-learning (2010) Morgan Kaufmann},
