n team Markov games (2002) Advances in Neural Information Processing System (NIPS-2002); (2003) Business Process Execution Language for Web Services, Version 1.1, , IBM, ftp://www6.software.ibm.com/software/developer/library/ws-bpel11. pdf, 2003.5; (2001) Business Process Modeling Language, , http://www.bpmi.org/specifications, Available from, esp, 2001.8; Burstein, M., Ankolenkar, A., (2002) DAML-S: Web Service Description for the Semantic Web, pp. 348-363. , Lecture Notes in Computer Science, 2342; Ermolayev, V., Keberle, N., Plaksin, S., Towards agent-based rational service composition: RACING approach (2003) Proceeding of the International Conference on Web Services Europe, , http://www.old.netobjectdays.org/pdf/03/papers/icws/28530167.pdf167-182, Erfurt, Germany; Thusijsaman, F., Optimality and equilibrium in stochastic games (1992) Centrum Voor Wiskunde en Information},
correspondence_address1={Cao, J.; Dept. of Computer Science and Engineering, , Shanghai, China; email: cao-jian@cs.sjtu.edu.cn},
sponsors={IEEE Computer Society (CS)},
